{
    "openapi": "3.0.0",
    "info": {
        "title": "Backend SAP-UI-5",
        "description": "API documentation for Backend SAP-UI-5",
        "version": "1.0.0"
    },
    "servers": [
        {
            "url": "/",
            "description": "Server"
        }
    ],
    "paths": {
        "/api/local-so-data": {
            "get": {
                "summary": "API to get data SO Scheduling H-1",
                "description": "T DATA1 dan T DATA2 dari hasil scheduling. Data telah dienkripsi dengan AES-256-CBC.\n\n### Cara Dekripsi Response (Contoh PHP):\n\n```php\n$secretKey = 'API_KEY_ANDA';\n$decodedPayload = base64_decode($response['encrypted_data']);\n\n$iv = substr($decodedPayload, 0, 16);\n$encryptedDatas = substr($decodedPayload, 16);\n\n$key = substr(hash('sha256', $secretKey, true), 0, 32);\n$jsonAsli = openssl_decrypt($encryptedDatas, 'aes-256-cbc', $key, 0, $iv);\n\n$data = json_decode($jsonAsli, true);\n```\n\n### Cara Dekripsi Response (Contoh Node.js / Javascript):\n\n```javascript\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\n\nconst secretKey = 'API_KEY_ANDA';\nconst encryptedPackage = response.encrypted_data; // Dari API\n\n// 1. Decode base64 payload\nconst buf = Buffer.from(encryptedPackage, 'base64');\n\n// 2. Ekstrak IV (16 bytes pertama) & sisa data terenkripsi\nconst iv = buf.subarray(0, 16);\nconst encryptedData = buf.subarray(16);\n\n// 3. Hash secretKey menjadi 32 bytes menggunakan SHA-256\nconst key = crypto.createHash('sha256').update(secretKey).digest();\n\n// 4. Proses Dekripsi AES-256-CBC\nconst decipher = crypto.createDecipheriv('aes-256-cbc', key, iv);\ndecipher.setAutoPadding(true);\n\nlet decrypted = decipher.update(encryptedData, undefined, 'utf8');\ndecrypted += decipher.final('utf8');\n\nconst data = JSON.parse(decrypted);\nconsole.log(data);\n```",
                "parameters": [
                    {
                        "name": "X-API-KEY",
                        "in": "header",
                        "required": true,
                        "schema": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "description": "Secret Key Authentication"
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "iv_werks",
                        "in": "query",
                        "required": true,
                        "schema": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "enum": ["3000", "2000"]
                        }
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "iv_auart",
                        "in": "query",
                        "required": true,
                        "schema": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "enum": ["ZOR2", "ZOR1"]
                        }
                    }
                ],
                "responses": {
                    "200": {
                        "description": "Success",
                        "content": {
                            "application/json": {
                                "schema": {
                                    "type": "object",
                                    "properties": {
                                        "success": {
                                            "type": "boolean",
                                            "example": true
                                        },
                                        "message": {
                                            "type": "string",
                                            "example": "Data successfully retrieved and encrypted."
                                        },
                                        "encrypted_data": {
                                            "type": "string",
                                            "description": "Base64 encoded string containing the IV and AES encrypted payload.",
                                            "example": "m+C2lO0b..."
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "401": {
                        "description": "Unauthorized - Missing or Invalid Secret Key",
                        "content": {
                            "application/json": {
                                "schema": {
                                    "type": "object",
                                    "properties": {
                                        "success": {
                                            "type": "boolean",
                                            "example": false
                                        },
                                        "message": {
                                            "type": "string",
                                            "example": "Unauthorized. Secret key is missing or invalid."
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "403": {
                        "description": "Forbidden - Invalid Parameters",
                        "content": {
                            "application/json": {
                                "schema": {
                                    "type": "object",
                                    "properties": {
                                        "success": {
                                            "type": "boolean",
                                            "example": false
                                        },
                                        "message": {
                                            "type": "string",
                                            "example": "Parameter iv_werks dan iv_auart tidak valid..."
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
